sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI
    participant Orchestrator
    participant Adapter as YouTube Adapter
    participant Enrichment
    participant LLM
    participant Corroboration
    participant Stats
    participant Synthesize

    User->>CLI: srp research "topic" "purpose"
    CLI->>Orchestrator: run_research(topic, purposes)
    Orchestrator->>Adapter: health_check()
    Adapter-->>Orchestrator: ok
    Orchestrator->>Adapter: search(query, limits)
    Adapter-->>Orchestrator: raw items
    Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: score + z-score → top-5
    Orchestrator->>Enrichment: enrich_top5(top5)
    Enrichment->>Adapter: fetch transcript
    Adapter-->>Enrichment: transcript text
    Enrichment->>LLM: summarise(transcript)
    LLM-->>Enrichment: 100-word summary
    Enrichment-->>Orchestrator: enriched top-5
    Orchestrator->>Corroboration: corroborate_top5(top5)
    Corroboration-->>Orchestrator: evidence snippets
    Orchestrator->>Stats: build_stats_summary(items)
    Stats-->>Orchestrator: statistical summaries
    Orchestrator->>Synthesize: build_packet(...)
    Synthesize-->>Orchestrator: ResearchPacket
    Orchestrator-->>CLI: ResearchPacket
    CLI->>User: Markdown summary + HTML report path
